From dc8c4cbf4d0596958277a81975ba29e339441583 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 12:22:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Redesign site with premium editorial studio look

Replace the generic dark purple/cyan SaaS-template aesthetic with a
distinctive brass/rust-on-obsidian visual system, Heebo typography,
editorial index-numbered sections, a connected process timeline, and a
real FINZO product mockup instead of an empty placeholder card. Adds
tasteful scroll-reveal micro-interactions (as progressive enhancement,
so content stays visible without JS) and a sticky header that solidifies
on scroll.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_018Mdw7sRHPQ5kNbmUnuxudU
